    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/greater-anglia-franchise-specific-agreement"/>
    <title>Greater Anglia</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please note that the Public Register of Franchise Agreements is updated on a quarterly basis and that the data held on the website may not be necessarily be the most current information held by the department. If you cannot find the information that you need, please contact us at &lt;a href="mailto:rail.publicregister@dft.gsi.gov.uk"&gt;rail.publicregister@dft.gsi.gov.uk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

